quran[88]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Swad. Nditsuba khu Ikurani eyili nende ametsulisio."
  38,2,"Halali Abakhayi bali mukhwilola nende obuyingani."
  38,3,"Ni emikanda chinga chia khwasishia imbeli wabu, mana nibalanga owubakhonya, ne ebise biokhuwonokokha biali biburire."
  38,4,"Ne bawuka mbu yabetsera omwikanyilisi okhurula mubo, mana nibaboola mbu: “Uno ni Omulosi Omubeyi muno."
  38,5,"Eh! Akholele Abanyasaye okhuba Nyasaye mulala yenyene! Toto kano ni amakhuwa khokhuchenyia muno.”"
  38,6,"Mana Abakhongo mubo nibarula nibababoolela mbu: “Tsie mana mwisumilisie khubanyasaye benyu. Toto endio nilwakenyekhana."
  38,7,"Efwe shikhwawulilakhwo kano mushima shiefu shiokhumalilikha tawe. Kano shineshindu tawe halali ni obuchishi butswa."
  38,8,"Mbu niye butswa weshilibwa amekanyilisio mwifwe?” Halali abo bali nende obukanakani khu amekanyilisio kanje, ne mana bashili okhupila eshinyasio shianje tawe."
  38,9,"Nohomba bali nende ebiachi bietsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, Owamaani, Khakaba?"
  38,10,"Nohomba bo bali nende obwami bwomwikulu nende khushialo, nende ebili hakari wabio? Khomana banine tsinjila tsiokhutsia eyo."
  38,11,"Okwo nikwo omukanda kwabalwani kulishililwa eyo mumikanda (chia abakhayi)."
  38,12,"Bayingana inyuma wabu Abandu ba Nuhu, nende babu A’di nende Firaun owali nende ebiumbashe."
  38,13,"Nende Thamud nende Abandu ba Luti nende Abandu bomumutsuru. Echo nichio emikanda."
  38,14,"Abo boosi bayingasia Abarumwa mana nibakhoyeshela eshinyasio."
  38,15,"Ne bano shiabalindangasa ni oluyoka lulala butswa olulali lwokhubukhamwo tawe."
  38,16,"Nabo baboolanga mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khurerere lwangu eshinyasio shiefu inyanga yeyindukho nishili okhuula.”"
  38,17,"Wisumilisie khukababoolanga ako, ne witsulile Omusumba wefu Daudi owamaani. Toto ye yali omunji wokhusaba eshileshelo."
  38,18,"Ne toto khwahotselesia ebikulu halala ninaye nibitsoomia ingolobe nende mumabwibwi halala ninaye."
  38,19,"Ne kata amayoni kakhung’asibwa emikanda nemikanda, koosi kali amehotselefu khuye."
  38,20,"Ne nikhumeta amaani obwami bubwe, ne nikhumuhelesia amachesi nende obumanyi bwokhubusia omuse."
  38,21,"Ne koo, lwakhulilakhwo olukano lwaabasoolani olwa baniina liisisi nibeinjila munzu yokhulamilamwo?"
  38,22,"Olwa benjila wa Daudi, naye narenga khubo, nibaboola mbu: “Olaria tawe, efwe khuli abasoolani babili, mulala wefu akoseele owashie, kho khukhalachile eshina khubwatoto, ne olakwila elubeka tawe, ne khulunjisie khunjila yobwatoto."
  38,23,"Toto uno ni Omusiani wefu, ali nende amakondi amakhasi amakhumi tisa nende tisa, nasi endisa nende likondi lilalasa lieshikhasi, mana aboolanga mbu: 'Mbelesia elilio elo ekhuruchile' (nasi shindenya tawe). Mana yashilile khumakhuwa.”"
  38,24,"Naboola mbu: “Toto ye akhukholeele obubii okhusaba likondi lilio okhumeta khukeke. Ne toto abeyisanga abanji bakholelananga obubii abeene khubeene, halali balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, ne nibatiti sa mubo.” Mana Daudi nalola mbu khumukholeele amatemo, nasaba eshileshelo khu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi, mana nakwa hasi okhwihotselesia khu Nyasaye wuwe nende okhumukalushila."
  38,25,"Mana nikhumuleshela ako, ne toto ye ewefu ali nende eshisaala shia hambi muno ninafu nende habundu halayi wokhukalukha."
  38,26,"Ewe Daudi, toto efwe khwakhukhola okhuba omwemelesi wefu khushialo, kho khalaka emise chia Abandu khubwatoto, ne olalonda obwikombi bwomwoyo bwakhukosia ehale nende injila ya Nyasaye tawe. Toto balia bakoranga ehale nende injila ya Nyasaye balinyoola eshinyasio eshilulu khulwa okhubula oluchendo khwabu mu Inyanga yokhubalilwa efikhole."
  38,27,"Ne shikhwaloonga likulu nende eshialo, nende ebili hakari wabio eshikhaya tawe. Ako ni amaparo ka balia abakhaya. Kho eshinyasio eshilulu shiomulilo shilinyoola balia Abakhaya."
  38,28,"Nohomba khukhole balia basubila babe shinga balia bakholanga amabii khushialo, nohomba khukhole abaria Nyasaye shinga abetsimbii?"
  38,29,"Eshitabu shino shakhwakhwishilia ewe ni sha tsikhabi tsinyinji kho banyoole okhupaara mutsinyaali tsiashio, ne abandu ba amachesi banyoole okhuwulila."
  38,30,"Ne khwahelesia Dawudi Suleiman yali Omusumba omulayi muno, toto ye yali omunji wokhukalushila Nyasaye."
  38,31,"Olwa yalolwesibwa mubise bya ingolobe (lasiri) tsinyumbu tsia tsimbiro mana khandi tsindai po."
  38,32,"Mana naboola mbu: “Toto esie ndachama ebindu ebilayi okhushila okhwitsulila Nyasaye wanje Omulesi"", okhula (tsifarasi etso) nitsikhamukha mushirima (Suleiman niyenya mbu atsilole khandi)."
  38,33,"""Tsikalusie khwisie.” Mana nachaka okhutsitilakhwo mwikosi nende khubilenje."
  38,34,"Ne toto khwatema Suleiman, nenikhura omubili khushisaala shishie, mana nakalukha okhusaba eshileshelo."
  38,35,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ndeshela, ne mbelesia obwaami bwomundu wundi alalinyoola inyuma wanje tawe. Toto ewe newe Omuwani watoto.”"
  38,36,"Mana nikhukhola omuyeka okhumurumushila, kwachendanga khubulomesi bubwe hosi hosi ayenya okhuula."
  38,37,"Mana nikhukhola amashetani okhumurumushila, koosi kombakhanga nende keyibilanga mumatsi."
  38,38,"Nende akaandi kaboyungwa khuminyororo."
  38,39,"Shino ni eshihanwa shiefu. Kho mana rusia nohomba shitiile, shibula eshichelo."
  38,40,"Ne toto ye ewefu ali nende eshisaala shia hambi muno nefwe, nende habundu halayi muno wokhukalukha."
  38,41,"Ne yitsulila Omusumba wefu Ayub, olwa yalanga Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mbu: “Toto esie Shetani yanderere obusinyifu nende obusandi.”"
  38,42,"Nyasaye namuboolela mbu: “Sieba hasi eshilenje shishio (isebele nirundukha hasi awo). Kano namatsi amanyifu kokhwisinga nende kokhunywa.”"
  38,43,"Mana nikhumuhelesia Abandu bebe nende abandi shinga abo, nende tsimbabaasi tsirula khwifwe, nende eshitsulisio khubaandu bobwongo."
  38,44,"“Ne bukula mumukhono kukwo liisaka omukhupile (omukhaye wuwo khulwokhwitsuba khwa wetsuba khumabii kayakhola), ne olafunaka eshitsubo tawe."" Toto khwamunyoola nali Omwifwiili, Omusumba Omulayi muno. Toto ye yali wokhukalukha khwifwe muno khukhusaba eshileshelo."
  38,45,"Ne yitsulila Omusumba wefu Ibrahim nende Is’haaq nende Yaqub bali ba amaani nende amachesi."
  38,46,"Toto efwe khwabalobola khulikhuwa lilayi muno liokhwitsulila mwikulu."
  38,47,"Ne toto abo bali khwifwe Mubandu abaule abalayi."
  38,48,"Ne yitsulila Ismail, nende Alyasa nende Dhul-kifli, ne abo boosi bali Mubandu abalayi."
  38,49,"Kano ni ametsulisio, ne toto bwene balia baria Nyasaye habundu wabu wokhukalukha aliba alayi muno."
  38,50,"Emikunda chomwikulu echilaliwa tawe, echiabekulilwa emiliango chiachio."
  38,51,"Omo baliyiekhamwo nibalaanga ebiamo ebinji nende ebinywebwa ebilayi po."
  38,52,"Ne baliba nabakhaye babu abalengangasa abasatsa babu butswa, abolubaka lulala."
  38,53,"Kano niko kamwalakwa [okhunyoola] inyanga yokhubalilwa ebikhole."
  38,54,"Toto kuno niko omukabo kwefu okulawetsaanga tawe."
  38,55,"Endio nilwa kaliba, ne toto balia baruumanga olwakho lwa Nyasaye amakalushilo kabu kaliba amabii."
  38,56,"Jahannam balinjilamwo, naho ni habundu abii muno wokhukonawo."
  38,57,"Endio nilwa kaliba, mana banywemwo amatsi kayia pa nende kamafila."
  38,58,"Nende ebinyasio bindi ngabino ebinji."
  38,59,"Kuno nikwo omukanda kulinjila halala ninanyu, balibula okhwinjisibwa obulayi. Toto abo balinjila mumulilo."
  38,60,"Baliboola mbu: “Enywe nenywe mubula amwinjila halayi, nenywe mwachila nikhunyoola eshinyasio, kho muli habundu abii muno wokhutong'a.”"
  38,61,"Baliboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, balia bachila nikhunyoola kano bameete eshinyasio amakhabi khabili mumulilo.”"
  38,62,"Mana ababii balia balireeba mbu: “Kabeele karie wakhulalolanga Abandu bakhwabalilanga mubabii mumulilo kuno?"
  38,63,"Koo, khwababayila nohomba tsimoni tsiefu nitsilalolanga tawe?"""
  38,64,"Toto khuno nokhusolana khwatoto khwa Abandu bomumuliro."
  38,65,"Boola mbu: “Esie endisa Omwikanyilisi, ne abulaho Nyasaye wundi tawe owulali Nyasaye mulala Owamani muno."
  38,66,"Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, nende bili hakari wabio, Owamaani muno, Omunji weshileshelo.”"
  38,67,"Boola mbu: “Kano ni amacheni amakhongo muno aka enywe mukhayanga."
  38,68,"Ka enywe mubula ninako oluchendo [enywe nanyu mukakhayanga]."
  38,69,"Shindali nende obumanyi bwa ebilonje ebikhongo bioluyali olwabiayingananga tawe."
  38,70,"Ndahebwa obufimbuli shichila esie endi Omwikanyilisi owa habulafu."
  38,71,"Olwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yaboolela Abamalaika mbu: 'Esie ndalalonga Omundu okhurula khuliloba."
  38,72,"Kho olwandalamukasia obulai, mana emufuremwo omwoyo okhurulana ninasi, kho murerere obweni bwenyu hasi.'”"
  38,73,"Mana Abamalaika boosi nibara hasi obweni halala."
  38,74,"Halali Iblisi nakhola obufuru, mana naba mubakhayi."
  38,75,"Nyasaye namureeba mbu: “Ewe Iblisi, shina shikhukayiile okhura hasi obweni khulwa shienonjele nende emikhono chianje? Okholele obufuru nohomba oli mubakhongo?”"
  38,76,"Iblisi naboola mbu: ""Esie endi omulayi muno okhumushila ye. Waloonga esie okhurulana khu muliro, naye nomuloonga okhurula khuliloba.”"
  38,77,"Nyasaye namuboolela mbu: “Mana rulamwo, ewe toto olonderwe."
  38,78,"Ne toto eshilaamo shianje shikhulikhwo okhula inyanga yomurungo.”"
  38,79,"Iblis naboola mbu: ""Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, mbelesia obwiyangu ndalafwa tawe okhula inyanga yokhulamusibwa mubafu."""
  38,80,"Nyasaye namuboolela mbu: “Mana oli mubahelesibwe obwiyangu."
  38,81,"Okhula ebise bieyinyanga imanyishe.”"
  38,82,"Iblis naboola mbu: “Nditsuba khumaani koko, toto nditsa okhubakosia boosi [Abana ba Adam]."
  38,83,"Halali Abasumba bobo abatswenulwa mubo.”"
  38,84,"Nyasaye naboola mbu: “Toto, ne emboolanga obwatoto."
  38,85,"Ndiliitsusia Jahannam khu ewe nende balia boosi balikhuloondakhwo mubo.”"
  38,86,"Boola mbu: “Esie shebarebanga omurungo kwosikwosi tawe nohomba esie shendi wokhunichilisia tawe."
  38,87,"Kano ni ametsulisio butswa khubiloonje bioosi."
  38,88,"Ne toto mulamanya amacheni kayo ahambi hano."""
